Class PropertyCollector

java.lang.Object
Services.PropertyCollector
@Layer(BACK_END) public class PropertyCollector extends Object
The PropertyCollector class is responsible for collecting and filtering property data from a list of districts. It provides methods to collect properties by owner, district, municipality, and parish, as well as methods to retrieve unique owner IDs and names of districts, municipalities, and parishes.
